Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.93,0:01:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved you because I could never reach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.81,0:02:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far I go... It's still the same sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.76,0:02:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the attack coming from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that... you've been hiding in the Abe all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm omnipresent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this world isn't mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a Secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came from a distant place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.19,0:02:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A place where neither Scub Coral or Secrets are present.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world where humans create energy and everything shines in a brilliant light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All's well that ends well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, how do I report this to Colonel Tanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something! Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Abe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Where did he come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maggie! Elena! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maggie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elena!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa told me with his final words that Truth was a Secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you use to corporate with Truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was all Nakamura from the Defense Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does Truth want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was indeed once a Secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Not Johansson's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johansson?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's lost himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth, just what do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an ally of the Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're on our side now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an ally of the Secrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're still on our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, still, you killed the President...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth has abnormally high trapar density surrounding himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could call it a trapar storm or perhaps whirlpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can overcome it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ao can see the waves of trapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not possible with his Nirvash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:05:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has no soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A machine having a soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? I can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elena!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I can't read the flow of the trapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it her body?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Plant Coral shouldn't have been reactivated...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Quartz don't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just destroy the Scub Coral!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect, Truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calculate an interception course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me that the Scub Corals are all interconnected?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it because Ao is Eureka's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for assisting us with the rescue effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it. We're glad to know you're all safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that report even mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is happening with our IFO pilots?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have returned, disgraced and ashamed! I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The acting president has approved of your return.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Ao?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He showed up on Iwato Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iwato Island...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:08:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where his girlfriend is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not his girlfriend! He said they're just childhood friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0150,,Truth is heading for the Okinawan Plant Coral.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0150,,The largest Quartz in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0150,,He really can't change the fact that he's a Secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0150,,No, he's going for a different reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait, what the hell did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sup, Elena!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like the new gear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off! Take it off right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or what? Are we going to have a threesome with Nirvash and Alleluia next?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you may as well give it a lion's chest and a tiger's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth is no longer a Secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth is no longer a Secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been that way for more than a decade now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ignoring me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said he's not himself anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't Secrets just antibodies that emerge automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to erase anything that doesn't belong in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider the antibody itself becoming infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coral Carriers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Allied Forces trained pilots who have the coral implanted in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what Hannah Mama reported about earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stanley knew about this all along, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Scub Coral is a colony of small life forms much like real corals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Scub Coral encounters an intelligent life form,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it might assimilate the life form in an attempt to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assimilate? Does that mean they cease to be humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago, Truth emerged to create a confluence explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Quartz suddenly disappeared and the Secret became confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He emerged to destroy the Quartz, but his target disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He would've kept on rampaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Scub Coral merged with the Secret and helped him stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why that child thinks that a world without the Scub is a right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to create that world himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight with Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.25,0:11:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people around Naru are dangerous elements because they're infected by the Scub.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru is just sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:12:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people downstairs said that her disease is spreading.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Scub infects people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you targeted Ao as a foreigner...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've moved on to Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people infected by the Scub are camping at the Plant Coral.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They claim they can hear the Scub's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that creepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how you draw the line between you and those who are different from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You changed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you've grown those things on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just some accessories?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is that Truth's fetish?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they say girls wear different stuff for guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you like Truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you've been thinking the whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you looked at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know, I met Mom and talked with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you see, I might've had a sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought that because you've protected me since we were little,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're like my sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister? Your sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hannah Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama? Now I'm your mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, we're going after Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll work together with the Triton.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought Team Harlequin was our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had to say so at that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were born from a human and the Scub Coral.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth is the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is weird... This shouldn't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Big Blue World guaranteed that it's safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't produce any abnormalities in the Coral Carriers from our experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Truth's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our observations suggest that the IFO Blanc called Canon, which has now merged with Truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is creating a space of extremely high trapar density around itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the trapar density rises, the coral in the Carriers go berserk,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Scub kills its host.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many Okinawans who are unaware that they're Coral Carriers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A carrier like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll all die if Truth's IFO gets close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! The Scub enters us to make us humans better!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was a sickness all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Scub granted me invisible wings that are inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that when the day the world is filled with trapar comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you and I would become equals, Ao... And our wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans and Scub Coral are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you drawing that line?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though you're not a carrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're not sure how it'll affect your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us and Ivica.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:16:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Secrets say they'll help too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stop him no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru, you haven't changed at all, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You protected me from the people who treated me as a foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Scub Coral populates the world, no one will think I'm different anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you understand that I haven't changed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:16:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't win against Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Nirvash doesn't have an Archetype.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? It doesn't sound like equipment upgrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When are they gonna kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A special emergency warning has been issued.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat. The Okinawan government has issued a special emergency warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Allied Forces will commence operations in the area,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so take refuge immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Refrain from using FPs and other trapar powered devices temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat. The Okinawan government has issued a special emergency warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come! Come, Truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A decade ago, the Japanese government \Nconsidered trapar mining to be too dangerous,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and tried to seal the Scub away by taking it under direct interior control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Okinawa resisted,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and used the help from the Americans to forcibly gain independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the results now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the apocalypse you guys chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IFOs?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Harlequin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liu! Lerato! Rajkumar! Don't let him get any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might want to trigger a confluence explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we can't just let him take the Quartz, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's an explosion here, the whole area from Okinawa to Taiwan will be affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth was reborn below the Generation Bleu HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he triggers a confluence explosion,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he might be able to heal himself using the Scub Coral's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:19:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to trust {\i1}him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give him a good scolding, Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how mad you become...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you change your form...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are still a Secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not. I don't care about the Scub Coral.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to destroy the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then are you the Scub Coral that invaded this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then are you a human? The son of Johansson?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not that either...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Body blow successful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elena, pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I must...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare the main cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.35,0:21:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only Truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.31,0:22:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no more over here too...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.34,0:22:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same wherever I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Scub Coral encountered the defenses and the planet died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven pillars...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Seventh Swell!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.07,0:22:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvash!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Nirvash.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eureka's calling us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.66,0:23:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be over... I can finally end it all now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.36,0:23:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Eureka?
